Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.51,0:12:00.28,Main,Takkun,0000,0000,0000,,O čem to mluvíš?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.28,0:12:01.04,Main,Otohime,0000,0000,0000,,Nevíš?
